headline: TXRH Bets on Unit Growth: Will 35 New Stores in 2026 Move the Needle?
summary: Texas Roadhouse plans about 35 new company-owned restaurants in 2026, betting steady unit growth can sustain momentum despite inflation and higher capital spending.
